                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "interaction",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A crawling hand can sense the vital essence of living and undead creatures within 30 feet. This sense can distinguish between the vitality energy animating living creatures and the void energy animating undead creatures, much as sight distinguishes color. However, a crawling hand can't see, so effects that depend on vision or seeing don't work on it.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
